title: Cher discusses the history of Hmong people and his experience adjusting to life in the U.S.

media:group.media:title: Cher discusses the history of Hmong people and his experience adjusting to life in the U.S.
media:group.media:description:
Cher, a participant in our “Being Asian in America” documentary, discusses the history of Hmong people and his experience adjusting to life in the U.S.

This video is part of our “Being Asian in America” project. 
Watch the full documentary here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIIvqJDv6_4 
For more on the project, visit https://www.pewresearch.org/BeingAsianInAmerica
